{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSDictionary","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set for the current device"}]}],"name":"tags"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags are key-value pairs that enable targeted push notifications based on user attributes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and behavior. Use tags to segment your audience and send personalized messages to specific"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user groups.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Supported Tag Types","anchor":"Supported-Tag-Types","type":"heading","level":2},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Example","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"String","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"city\": \"New York\"","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integer"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"age\": 25","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Numeric values","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Boolean","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"isPremium\": true"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"True\/false values","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"List"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"interests\": [\"sports\", \"music\"]","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Arrays of strings","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Date"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"lastPurchase\": Date()"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"NSDate objects"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update user profile tags after account changes:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func updateUserTags(for user: User) {","        var tags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_id\": user.id,","            \"email_verified\": user.isEmailVerified,","            \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_date\": user.createdAt,","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        \/\/ Add subscription info if premium","        if let subscription = user.subscription {","            tags[\"subscription_tier\"] = subscription.tier.rawValue","            tags[\"subscription_expiry\"] = subscription.expiryDate","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = true","        } else {","            tags[\"is_premium\"] = false","        }","","        \/\/ Add user preferences","        if !user.interests.isEmpty {","            tags[\"interests\"] = user.interests","        }","","        \/\/ Add location if available","        if let location = user.location {","            tags[\"country\"] = location.country","            tags[\"city\"] = location.city","            tags[\"timezone\"] = location.timezone","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags(tags)","        Logger.debug(\"User tags updated: \\(tags.keys.joined(separator: \", \"))\")","    }","","    func trackPurchase(product: Product, amount: Decimal) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"last_purchase_date\": Date(),","            \"last_purchase_amount\": NSDecimalNumber(decimal: amount),","            \"last_purchase_category\": product.category,","            \"total_purchases\": incrementTag(\"total_purchases\")","        ])","    }","}"]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"role":"symbol","title":"setTags:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setTags:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setTags:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"}],"role":"symbol","title":"setTags:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets user tags for device segmentation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.